## Get user by id [/api/users/{id}]

### Get a specific user by their MBI identifier [GET]

+ Request

    + Headers
    
            Accept: application/json

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "id": "12456"
                "name": "Joe Bloggs",
                "username": "loremipsum1"
            }

## Create a new user [/api/users]

### Create a new user [POST]

+ Request

    + Headers
    
            Accept: application/json
            Content-Type: application/json
    
    + Body
    
            {
                "firstName": "Anew",
                "lastName": "User",
                "username": "anewuser100",
                "emailAddress": "anewuser100@anewuser.com",
                "dOB": "1990-05-17",
            }
            
+ Response 201 (application/json)

            {
                "id": "123456789",
                "createdAt": "2015-10-13 00:00:00"
            }
            
            

+ Response 200 (application/json)

